g.text: System Sequence Diagram - US 3.2.2: Auto-load Internal Authorization Role After Authentication (Frontend Only)
Opens Google login window\nwith client_id, redirect_uri, scope
Send idToken to get user details
401 Unauthorized\n{ error: "User has no assigned role" }
Display error: "User has no assigned role. Access denied."
Display error: "User account is Inactive. Access denied."
200 OK\n{ email, name, foto, role, status }
setToken(idToken, name, email, picture, role, status)
Store in localStorage:\ntoken, userName, email,\npicture, role, status
Display role-based menu and redirect to role page
